{"id":47394,"date":"2025-04-09T14:04:20","date_gmt":"2025-04-09T14:04:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/?p=47394"},"modified":"2025-04-18T18:17:51","modified_gmt":"2025-04-18T18:17:51","slug":"help-for-myself","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/addiction-help\/help-for-myself\/","title":{"rendered":"Addiction Help for Myself"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"47394\" class=\"elementor elementor-47394\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a0ae29d e-flex e-con-boxed cmsmasters-block-default e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1a0ae29d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-69c86bdc cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"69c86bdc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1>Addiction Help for Myself<\/h1>\n<p><strong>When You Know Something Needs to Change But You&#8217;re Not Sure Where to Start.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Reaching out for help with an addiction can feel overwhelming. Maybe you\u2019ve thought about rehab before, or perhaps this is your first time even considering it. Either way, you\u2019re here and that&#8217;s a huge step.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>At Abbington House, we support people who are ready to take a step toward recovery, even if they\u2019re not sure exactly what that step should look like. You don\u2019t have to be absolutely certain, but you have to be open to receiving help.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why People Come to Us<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Most of the people we work with have tried to stop drinking or using before. Some have had periods of sobriety. Others feel stuck in a pattern they can\u2019t explain or escape. For others, an ultimatum from a loved one has pushed them to seek treatment.<\/p>\n<p>You might be here because:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item --><\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You feel like you&#8217;re losing control of your drinking or drug use<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You&#8217;re exhausted by the cycle of guilt, secrecy, or shame<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You&#8217;re worried about how this is affecting your work, relationships or health<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You want to feel like yourself again, but don\u2019t know how.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>You\u2019re not alone in this. And you don\u2019t need to have all the answers right now. Our role is to help you make a decision without judgment.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How We Can Support You in Recovery<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Abbington House is a trauma-informed rehab in Hertfordshire that offers private, residential treatment for addiction. But more than that, we offer space to share, to reconnect with who you are underneath the struggle.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Our approach includes:<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item --><\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>One-to-one therapy<\/strong> tailored to you<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Trauma-informed care<\/strong>, acknowledging your past without defining you by it<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Group support<\/strong> that feels safe, grounded, and rooted in human connection<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Gentle<\/strong> <strong>daily structure<\/strong>, routines, and practices that bring calm and clarity<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>A home-like setting<\/strong>, with warmth and dignity in every room, and in every meal that we share together.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>You may not realise it yet, but a better version of you is waiting.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/residential-rehab\/\">See what makes our programme different<\/a> \u2192<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What If I&#8217;m Not Ready?<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>That\u2019s okay.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>We speak to people every day who are still deciding. Some call to discuss their options and others just need reassurance that change is possible.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>We won\u2019t rush you into making a decision and won&#8217;t push you into treatment. We\u2019ll listen, and if you want, we\u2019ll help you explore whether Abbington House feels right for you.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>It all starts with one conversation.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What to Expect When You Call<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>We know this isn\u2019t easy, so we\u2019ve made the first step feel as stress-free as possible.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>When you call:<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} --><\/p>\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item --><\/ol>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>You\u2019ll speak to someone kind, respectful, and experienced (often someone who\u2019s been through recovery themselves)<!-- wp:list-item --><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/li>\n<li>We\u2019ll invite you to share &#8211; but only what you\u2019re comfortable with<!-- wp:list-item --><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/li>\n<li>We\u2019ll talk through what you need and what your options are<!-- wp:list-item --><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/li>\n<li>If you\u2019d like to move forward, we\u2019ll walk you through every detail.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:list --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>You can call, email or chat with us on Livechat if you feel more comfortable.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/contact-us\/\">Contact Abbington House<\/a> \u2192<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Real Stories, Real People<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>Many of our team members have been through addiction and recovery themselves. We know the courage it takes to ask for help because we\u2019ve been in this very position before. We know what a difference the right support can make.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:html --><\/p>\n<div id=\"06xfo7he\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<p><script src=\"https:\/\/www.doctify.com\/get-script?widget_container_id=06xfo7he&amp;type=horizontal-widget&amp;tenant=athena-uk&amp;language=en&amp;profileType=practice&amp;layoutType=layoutXL&amp;slugs=abbington-house&amp;background=white\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:html --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:separator --><\/p>\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\n<p><!-- \/wp:separator --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ready When You Are<\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>You don\u2019t need to wait for a rock bottom moment. If you\u2019re questioning your drinking or drug use, or if something is telling you it\u2019s time for change, then that\u2019s enough.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>We&#8217;re here to talk, whenever you\u2019re ready.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c802e3e cmsmasters-icon-arrangement-together cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button\" data-id=\"c802e3e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"cmsmasters-button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__button-container\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__button-container-inner\"><a href=\"tel:01438583222\" class=\"cmsmasters-button-link elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__button cmsmasters-icon-view-default cmsmasters-icon-shape- cmsmasters-button-size-sm\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__content-wrapper cmsmasters-align-icon-left\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-phone\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-button__text\">Call Us Now<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you are looking for addiction treatment for yourself, this guide will help you prepare for the journey ahead. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":45495,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[113],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-47394","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-addiction-help"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/47394","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=47394"}],"version-history":[{"count":30,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/47394\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":48088,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/47394\/revisions\/48088"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/45495"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=47394"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=47394"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=47394"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}